{
  "name": "Monitor spend with HTTP / REST API and Gmail without manual work",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "days",
              "daysInterval": 1,
              "triggerAtHour": 6
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "f0d9ab00-d465-410d-bdde-fdea65068dbd",
      "name": "Schedule Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        320,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "5ff5f7b0-ec96-427a-a3cf-2da6f0c5f043",
              "name": "receivedAt",
              "value": "={{ $now.toISO() }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "84fc4ddc-ff2a-4ef4-ab14-fd48aea13d25",
              "name": "isValid",
              "value": "={{ $json ? true : false }}",
              "type": "boolean"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "ab977da0-5948-4bdf-b6e8-5cf2b232bd14",
      "name": "Validate Input",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [
        560,
        300
      ],
      "notes": "Validate & normalize the input before downstream steps (§9.1)."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://data.example.org/latest.json",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "932c0f26-bc07-4337-b87f-9c670afccaad",
      "name": "Fetch Data",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        800,
        300
      ],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "typeValidation": "loose",
            "version": 2
          },
          "combinator": "and",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "2bd0f7e1-8ac2-489f-b08a-0a5cf7799187",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.amount }}",
              "rightValue": "open",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "39ac6ae3-c3b3-4908-8c4a-7f99e0f77174",
      "name": "Route on Condition",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        1040,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "message",
        "operation": "send",
        "sendTo": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "Automated update",
        "message": "={{ $json.summary }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "fd369acc-3f79-44a2-891c-997127a96ce3",
      "name": "Send Gmail Message",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.gmail",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        1280,
        300
      ],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "27c7c6a6-e81a-4a21-994b-6cc7837fe72a",
      "name": "Skip (No Action)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.noOp",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1280,
        500
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Monitor spend with HTTP / REST API and Gmail without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Threshold Monitoring\n**Trigger:** Scheduled\n**Integrations:** HTTP / REST API, Gmail\n\nImport, add your credentials, then adjust parameters. Original FlowDex template.",
